		<dict>
			<key>NSAllowsArbitraryLoads</key>
			<true/>
			<key>NSAllowsLocalNetworking</key>
			<true/>
		</dict>
		<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI uses the camera to take photos or videos you choose to share in chats. For example, you can snap a photo of a document and attach it to a message.</string>
		<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI uses the microphone to record voice messages and enable voice-to-text in chats. For example, when you hold the mic button in a conversation, we capture your speech to send as an audio message or transcript.</string>
		<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI uses your location to keep location-aware chats and prompts up to date. When enabled, your current location may be sent to and stored with your account on your connected server.</string>
		<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI uses your location to keep location-aware chats and prompts up to date. When enabled, your current location may be sent to and stored with your account on your connected server.</string>
		<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI needs access to your photo library so you can select existing images or videos to share in chats. For example, you can pick a screenshot to include in a conversation.</string>
		<key>NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription</key>
		<string>众小智AI uses on-device speech recognition so you can dictate messages hands‑free. Your speech is converted to text on your device when available.</string>
